name: Stygian Street Patrol
desc: If this card destroys a monster by battle and sends it to the GY: Inflict damage to your opponent equal to the original Level of that monster in the GY x 100. You can banish this card from your GY; Special Summon 1 Fiend monster with 2000 or less ATK from your hand.

ocg.pack: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's World Championship 2010: Reverse of Arcadia Game Guide promotional card
